dct_title_s: Geologic map of the Soberanes Point and Mount Carmel quadrangles, Monterey County, California
dct_alternative_sm: Soberanes Point and Mount Carmel map
Geology Soberanes Point and Mount Carmel quadrangles
dct_description_sm: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr.; edited by John A. Minch.
Relief shown by contours and spot heights.
"Topographic base map from available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangle Soberanes Point, CA 1995, NIMA 1656 IV NW -- Series V895; Mount Carmel, CA 1947."
Includes quadrangle location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, and index to sources of geology.
Includes "pertinent references", most recent published in 1999.
